hopobject.body: Will I have to work on Saturdays? duloxetine drugs.com The Giants needed Mr. Perfect Game, but an impostor took the mound, someone with no command and minimal confidence. It was excruciating to watch as Bochy got the bullpen up during the fourth batter Cain faced. The pitcher had to be injured, went the prevailing sentiment, because it was the first time in 254 starts that he failed to get out of the first inning. This couldn't happen without a dire reason to explain it.
